Working at ProgressiveWe celebrate the person you are, the ideas you bring, and the energy you invest





They say if you choose a job you love, you’ll never work a day in your life. To many of us at Progressive, that quote rings true.
There’s a reason that people have worked here for years and years and years. It’s because Progressive is a special type of place:

Where taking chances and pushing innovation is a way of life
Where you don’t stop until a job is finished
Where hard work is celebrated and rewarded
Where you can meet interesting people who can teach you amazing things

It’s not window-dressing or feel-good recruiting language. It's the way of life for our more-than-28,000 employees.
We invite you to learn a little more about our culture, our locations, and the many benefits and other perks you can enjoy as a Progressive employee.
And join our Talent Network to learn more about our company, and receive monthly updates about working here.



