Workforce Management exists to increase our ability to answer a phone call and making sure that we are here and available when our customers call and being able to influence that is amazing. My work environment is very flexible. I am able to balance my work and life, meaning, I am a single mom, and so sometimes I am called to assist with a PTA function or being able to take my daughters to a doctor. I'm able to work with my manager to be able to do that.]


